    <title>hexo之NexT主题设置</title>
    <link href="http://wjh624.github.io/2018/10/02/hexo%E4%B9%8BNexT%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE/"/>
    <id>http://wjh624.github.io/2018/10/02/hexo之NexT主题设置/</id>
    <published>2018-10-02T05:51:13.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-10-11T14:38:45.802Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>一些完善和美化hexo-NexT主题的方法</p><a id="more"></a><blockquote class="blockquote-center">Table of Contents</blockquote> <p><ul class="markdownIt-TOC"><li><a href="#%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9-next-%E7%9A%84%E5%AD%90%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98">选择 NexT 的子主题</a></li><li><a href="#%E4%BE%A7%E8%BE%B9%E6%A0%8F%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5">侧边栏社交链接</a></li><li><a href="#toc-%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE">TOC 设置</a></li><li><a href="#%E5%9C%A8%E5%8F%B3%E4%B8%8A%E8%A7%92%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA-fork-me-on-github">在右上角显示 fork me on github</a></li><li><a href="#%E6%9B%B4%E6%94%B9%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E5%AE%BD%E5%BA%A6">更改内容区域宽度</a></li><li><a href="#%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E5%86%85%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F">修改文章内链接文本样式</a></li><li><a href="#%E5%9C%A8%E6%AF%8F%E7%AF%87%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E6%9C%AB%E5%B0%BE%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E6%9C%AC%E6%96%87%E7%BB%93%E6%9D%9F%E6%A0%87%E8%AE%B0">在每篇文章末尾统一添加“本文结束”标记</a></li><li><a href="#%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E8%A1%8C%E5%86%85%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%9D%97%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F">自定义行内代码块样式</a></li><li><a href="#%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB%E9%87%8F%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD">添加文章阅读量统计功能</a></li><li><a href="#%E4%B8%BB%E9%A1%B5%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E9%98%B4%E5%BD%B1%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C">主页文章添加阴影效果</a></li><li><a href="#%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD">实现统计功能</a></li><li><a href="#%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F">修改字体大小</a></li></ul></p><p>说明：以下文段中，站点配置文件是指根目录下的 _config 文件，主题配置文件是指 themes/next 目录下的 _config 文件</p><h2 id="选择-next-的子主题"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#选择-next-的子主题"></a> 选择 NexT 的子主题</h2><ul><li><p>更改主题配置文件</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#scheme: Muse</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#scheme: Mist</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">scheme:</span> <span class="string">Pisces</span> <span class="comment"># 注意此处scheme前不能加空格</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="侧边栏社交链接"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#侧边栏社交链接"></a> 侧边栏社交链接</h2><ul><li><p>更改主题配置文件，找到 <code>Social links</code></p></li><li><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">social:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  GitHub:</span> <span class="attr">https://github.com/wjh624</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">github</span> <span class="comment"># || 后面是图标的代号，一定要加上</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  Csdn:</span> <span class="attr">https://me.csdn.net/hz2217</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">copyright</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  E-Mail:</span> <span class="attr">mailto:wangjh624@gmail.com</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">envelope</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>设置相关图标，还是在当前文件下，找到 <code>social_icons</code>，图标的代号要在<a href="https://fontawesome.com/icons?from=io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">图标库</a>里找，拷贝过来就行</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">social_icons:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  GitHub:</span> <span class="string">github</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  Csdn:</span> <span class="string">copyright</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  icons_only:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  transition:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="toc-设置"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#toc-设置"></a> TOC 设置</h2><ul><li><p>我们都知道，在一般的markdown编辑器中，[TOC]是代表目录的，但是github博客网站渲染不出来，这时候就需要相关设置</p></li><li><p>TOC 是 Table of Contents 的缩写</p></li><li><p>安装</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm un hexo-renderer-marked --save <span class="comment"># 这个好像是关闭hexo本身的渲染，如果你有一天不需要这个插件了，要将.deploy_git文件删除，然后用hexo d才能重新正确上传并加载网站</span></span><br><span class="line">npm i hexo-renderer-markdown-it-plus --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>在站点配置文件如下，末端加上</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">markdown_it_plus:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">     highlight:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">     html:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">     xhtmlOut:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">     breaks:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">     langPrefix:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">     linkify:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">     typographer:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">     quotes:</span> <span class="string">“”‘’</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">     pre_class:</span> <span class="string">highlight</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>但是弊端是还是只能识别 @[TOC]，而无法识别 [TOC]</p></li><li><p>需要注意的一点是<strong>一定要从二级标题开始写起</strong>，一级标题应该默认作为文章标题而不会渲染，所以 <code>[TOC]</code> 中并不会出现一级标题。如果你想使用这个功能，就不要使用一级标题 <code>#</code></p></li></ul><h2 id="在右上角显示-fork-me-on-github"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#在右上角显示-fork-me-on-github"></a> 在右上角显示 fork me on github</h2><ul><li>点击<a href="https://github.com/blog/273-github-ribbons" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这里</a>或者<a href="http://tholman.com/github-corners/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这里</a>挑选自己喜欢的样式，并复制代码</li><li>粘贴刚才复制的代码到<code>themes/next/layout/_layout.swig</code>文件中(放在<code>&lt;div class=&quot;headband&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</code>的下面)，并把<code>href</code>改为你的github地址</li></ul><h2 id="更改内容区域宽度"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#更改内容区域宽度"></a> <a href="http://fengdi.org/2017/08/06/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">更改内容区域宽度</a></h2><h2 id="修改文章内链接文本样式"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#修改文章内链接文本样式"></a> 修改文章内链接文本样式</h2><ul><li><p>修改文件 <code>themes\next\source\css\_common\components\post\post-type.styl</code>，在末尾添加如下css样式</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// 文章内链接文本样式</span><br><span class="line">.post-body p a&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  color: #8a2be2;</span><br><span class="line">  border-bottom: none;</span><br><span class="line">  border-bottom: 1px solid #8a2be2;</span><br><span class="line">  &amp;:hover &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    color: #8a2be2;</span><br><span class="line">    border-bottom: none;</span><br><span class="line">    border-bottom: 1px solid #8a2be2;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="在每篇文章末尾统一添加本文结束标记"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#在每篇文章末尾统一添加本文结束标记"></a> 在每篇文章末尾统一添加“本文结束”标记</h2><ul><li><p>在路径<code>F:\Hexo\themes\next\layout\_macro</code>下，新建一个文件<code>passage-end-tag.swig</code>,文件内容中添加以下代码：</p><figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;<span class="selector-tag">div</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;% if not is_index %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;div style="text-align:center; color: #00CD00; font-size:14px;</span><br><span class="line">        "&gt;------------------------------------------ The End ------------------------------------------&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;% endif %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="自定义行内代码块样式"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#自定义行内代码块样式"></a> 自定义行内代码块样式</h2><ul><li><p>打开 <code>\themes\next\source\css\_custom\custom.styl</code> 向里面加入：(颜色可以自己定义)</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// Custom styles.</span></span><br><span class="line">code &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    color: #ff7600;</span><br><span class="line">    background: #fbf7f8;</span><br><span class="line">    margin: <span class="number">2</span>px;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 大代码块的自定义样式</span></span><br><span class="line">.highlight, pre &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    margin: <span class="number">5</span>px <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    padding: <span class="number">5</span>px;</span><br><span class="line">    border-radius: <span class="number">3</span>px;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">.highlight, code, pre &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    border: 1px solid #d6d6d6;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>代码块行号，主题配置文件中</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">highlight:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  line_number: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  auto_detect: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  tab_replace:</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="添加文章阅读量统计功能"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#添加文章阅读量统计功能"></a> <a href="https://notes.doublemine.me/2015-10-21-%E4%B8%BANexT%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB%E9%87%8F%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD.html#%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AELeanCloud" target="_blank" rel="noopener">添加文章阅读量统计功能</a></h2><h2 id="主页文章添加阴影效果"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#主页文章添加阴影效果"></a> 主页文章添加阴影效果</h2><ul><li><p>打开<code>\themes\next\source\css\_custom\custom.styl,</code>向里面加入</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 主页文章添加阴影效果</span></span><br><span class="line">.post &#123;</span><br><span class="line">margin-top: <span class="number">60</span>px;</span><br><span class="line">margin-bottom: <span class="number">60</span>px;</span><br><span class="line">padding: <span class="number">25</span>px;</span><br><span class="line">    -webkit-box-shadow: <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">5</span>px rgba(<span class="number">202</span>, <span class="number">203</span>, <span class="number">203</span>, <span class="number">.5</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    -moz-box-shadow: <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">5</span>px rgba(<span class="number">202</span>, <span class="number">203</span>, <span class="number">204</span>, <span class="number">.5</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="实现统计功能"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#实现统计功能"></a> 实现统计功能</h2><ul><li><p>在根目录下安装 <code>hexo-wordcount</code>，运行</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-wordcount --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>主题配置文件设置参数如下如下</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">post_wordcount:</span><br><span class="line">  item_text: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  wordcount: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  min2read: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>注意此时底部虽然有字数统计，但是没有 <code>|</code> 符号，需要在<code>\themes\next\layout\css\_partials\footer.swig</code>中加</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% <span class="keyword">if</span> theme.footer.powered and theme.footer.theme.enable %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;span <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"post-meta-divider"</span>&gt;|<span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endif %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="修改字体大小"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#修改字体大小"></a> 修改字体大小</h2><ul><li><p>打开<code>\themes\next\source\css\ _variables\base.styl</code>文件，将<code>$font-size-base</code>改成<code>16px</code>，如下所示：</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$font-size-base = <span class="number">16</span>px</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul>]]></content>
    
